snippet: Serena Williams overcame a shaky start and two service breaks to beat Coco Vandeweghe, 7-5, 6-3, in Stanford, Calif., for her second straight Bank of the West Classic title.
abstract: Serena Williams wins her second straight Bank of the West Classic title; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams overcame a shaky start and two service breaks to beat Coco Vandeweghe, 7-5, 6-3, in Stanford, Calif., for her second straight Bank of the West Classic title.

headline.seo: Serena Williams Wins at Stanford in Final Olympic Tuneup
